      ],
      "summary": "Bhuvaneswari Subramani, Chief Cloud Evangelist at Intuitive.ai, is a passionate technophile and strategic leader in multi-cloud migration, application modernization, and end-to-end development. She specializes in cloud service delivery, strategic alliances, and sales enablement, with deep expertise in Infrastructure-as-Code, DevOps, CI/CD, Agentic AI and AI-DLC. She also drives global outreach, mentors leaders, and bridges the gap between industry and academia. A self-made woman in tech, she has been recognized globally: - AWS re:Invent 2018 Diversity Scholar (https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/publicsector/meet-the-women-building-aws-technical-communities-around-the-world/) - AWS Community Hero (2019–2020), AWS DevTools Hero (from 2020 onwards) and featured in AWS Developer Story (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fOURKkUdtv0) - Honoured as AWS Hero of the Year 2022 at APJ Summit, Bangkok - Dr. Werner Vogel's Now Go Build Award 2022 Awardee - Spotlight in AWS Global Summits Video 2025 & early contributor to #AIDLC - Led the Navy Blue team in Road to ReInvent 2025 Hackathon, winning the title with $100K - She co-leads the AWS User Group Bengaluru (https://awsugblr.in/) and AWS WomenInTech India (https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-women-in-tech-india/), speaks at TEDx, global tech conferences, and universities, and blogs at https://bhuvana.saryoo.com Connect to collaborate on cloud innovation, leadership, and inclusive tech communities.",
